{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_clmyga4rwtixtmd98moz","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"580740512","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/work/tokenwarden-docs-from-code-1/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","content":"# Cache API\n\nA simple in-memory cache implementation using `Map`.\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates and returns a new cache instance with methods for storing and retrieving key-value pairs.\n\n```js\nexport function createCache() {\n  const values = new Map()\n  return {\n    get(key) { return values.get(key) },\n    set(key, value) { values.set(key, value); return value },\n    delete(key) { return values.delete(key) },\n    clear() { values.clear() }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves the value associated with the specified key. Returns `undefined` if no value is found for the key.\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `key` - The key to look up\n\n**Returns:** The cached value, or `undefined` if not found\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value in the cache under the specified key.\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `key` - The key to store the value under\n- `value` - The value to cache\n\n**Returns:** The value that was set\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves the value associated with the specified key from the cache.\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `key` - The key to delete\n\n**Returns:** `true` if a value was removed, `false` if the key did not exist\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n\n**Returns:** `undefined`\n"}}],"model":"qwen/qwen3.5-9b","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5371,"output_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":5350},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4ac672c5-5748-4793-8b9a-0e64df314d86","uuid":"9435a2af-f3ad-4223-b5e8-a65720dc80ea","timestamp":"2026-07-22T23:59:53.284Z"}
